Meatloaf Recipe with the Best Glaze
Prep Time: 10 minutes
Cook Time: 1 hour
Total Time: 1 hour

Author: Valentina Ablaev
Skill Level: Easy
Cost to Make: $10-$12
Keyword: meatloaf, meatloaf recipe Cuisine: American
Course: Dinner, Main Course Calories: 344 kcal
Servings: 8 servings

Ingredients Meatloaf Ingredients:
2 Ibs ground beef 85% or 90% lean 1 med onion finely chopped
2 large eggs
3 garlic cloves minced
3 Thsp ketchup
3 Thsp fresh parsley finely chopped 3/4 cup Panko breadcrumbs
143 cup milk
